      "side": 1,
      "message": "This uses a boolean lock (internalUpdateInProgress) to distinguish internal vs external sets. An alternative pattern (used in https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/dbus-sensors/+/90189 PS2 for PowerCap) is register_property with explicit setter+getter callbacks, where the BMC updates its own member and the getter returns it — no flag needed.\nBoth work, but consistency across the codebase may be worth considering.",
