      "writtenOn": "2026-05-24T08:43:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "On Set failure, the optimistic pending property stays stale until the next Get polling cycle (~30s). That\u0027s long enough for a user to observe the \"updated\" pending, trigger a GPU reset, then find ECC mode didn\u0027t change as expected. \nConsider triggering update() on Set failure to refresh pending from hardware sooner.",
